      "options": [
        "A. Deepened rationalization",
        "B. Capability",
        "C. Systemic opportunity",
        "D. Financial motivation"
      ],
      "correct": 1,
      "justification_correct": "The Fraud Diamond, developed by David Wolfe and Dana Hermanson, adds 'capability'—the competencies, authority, and trust necessary to commit fraud successfully. (CFE Fraud Examiners Manual)",
